{"tid":2006883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共：承認重用口罩只作一般用途 進出高危區域應使用外科口罩","createTime":"2020-05-08T05:26:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T05:34:09.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6b1b1f20cbb2fbf1f2c5d28174e439e1ea8a2436","tid":2006883,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T05:26:57.000Z","msg":"陳肇始：重用口罩只作一般用途而非醫學用<br />\n08.05.2020 13:12<br />\n<br />\n醫學界立法會議員陳沛然在衛生事務委員會上，表達關注市民配戴政府派發的可重用口罩，若遇到懷疑確診感染新型冠狀病毒的人士，應該如何消毒口罩。食物及衛生局長陳肇始回應指，重用口罩只作一般用途，而非醫學用途，如果去醫院或醫療機構，應該配戴適用的口罩，包括一次性的外科口罩或N95口罩等。<br />\n<br />\n另外，陳肇始回應提問時說，當局對利用酒店作為檢疫中心有保留，認為現有設施，在感染控制及空氣流轉方面，已經適合用作檢疫。她又預料，迪士尼樂園旁的竹篙灣政府土地，7月將會落成約700至800個檢疫單位，期望有助盡快騰出火炭駿洋邨給等待上樓的市民。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1286047&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1286047%26csid%3D261_341&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0OgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=f34eeecd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1286047&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"d6e3a8d894c51e3157d878f44b231cad704934a6","tid":2006883,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T05:32:50.000Z","msg":"你睇下呢個垃圾政府<br />\n無一樣野做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9bfc804dbf04f6ee9318b14ae69364481398d46","tid":2006883,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T05:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70cae2d2cb73fa0d8833b1322795ac0fe4df00dc","tid":2006883,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T05:34:09.000Z","msg":"派完先話冇用 玩郵差"}]}